// Demo card texts
'This product converts voice into text in real time, using AI to remove filler words, fix grammar, and restructure sentences for clarity.':{fr:'Ce produit convertit la voix en texte en temps reel, avec l\'IA pour supprimer les hesitations.',de:'Dieses Produkt wandelt Sprache in Echtzeit in Text um.',es:'Este producto convierte voz en texto en tiempo real.',it:'Questo prodotto converte la voce in testo in tempo reale.',zh:'这个产品将语音实时转换为文字，用 AI 去除冗余、修正语法、优化句子。'},
'Dictate once, rewrite for any platform. Watch how VoiceNote transforms the same voice input into different formats:':{fr:'Dictez une fois, reecrivez pour chaque plateforme. Regardez VoiceNote transformer :',de:'Einmal diktieren, fur jede Plattform umschreiben:',es:'Dicta una vez, reescribe para cada plataforma:',it:'Detta una volta, riscrivi per ogni piattaforma:',zh:'说一次，为任何平台重写。看看 VoiceNote 如何转化：'},
'Um, so basically I think we should consider maybe extending the deadline for the project because, you know, like, we\'re still waiting on some feedback from the client and the design team hasn\'t finished their revisions yet and honestly we need more time to make it, like, actually good instead of rushing it out...':{fr:'Euh, donc je pense qu\'on devrait prolonger le delai d\'une semaine, parce qu\'on attend des retours client...',de:'Ah, also ich denke wir sollten die Frist um eine Woche verlangern, weil wir noch auf Feedback warten...',es:'Eh, creo que deberiamos extender el plazo una semana, porque esperamos comentarios del cliente...',it:'Ehm, penso che dovremmo estendere la scadenza di una settimana, perche aspettiamo feedback...',zh:'呃，我觉得应该把截止日期延期一周，因为还在等客户反馈，设计团队也没完成修改...'},
'We need to extend the project deadline by one week due to delayed client feedback and required design revisions.':{fr:'Nous devons prolonger le delai d\'une semaine en raison du retard des retours clients.',de:'Wir mussen die Frist um eine Woche verlangern.',es:'Necesitamos extender el plazo una semana.',it:'Dobbiamo estendere la scadenza di una settimana.',zh:'由于客户反馈延迟，我们需要延长截止日期一周。'},
'I propose extending the project deadline due to outstanding client feedback and ongoing design revisions. Additional time will ensure we deliver work that meets our quality standards.':{fr:'Je propose de prolonger le delai d\'une semaine en raison des retours clients en attente.',de:'Ich schlage vor, die Frist um eine Woche zu verlangern.',es:'Propongo extender el plazo una semana por comentarios pendientes.',it:'Propongo di estendere la scadenza di una settimana per feedback in sospeso.',zh:'由于客户反馈和设计修改尚未完成，建议延期一周。'},
'Extend project deadline by 7 days':{fr:'Prolonger le delai de 7 jours',de:'Frist um 7 Tage verlangern',es:'Extender plazo 7 dias',it:'Estendere scadenza 7 giorni',zh:'延期一周'},
'Awaiting final client feedback':{fr:'En attente du feedback client',de:'Warten auf Kundenfeedback',es:'Esperando comentarios del cliente',it:'In attesa feedback cliente',zh:'等待客户最终反馈'},
