'FAQ':{fr:'FAQ',de:'FAQ',es:'FAQ',it:'FAQ',zh:'常见问题'},
'How does the free trial work?':{fr:'Comment fonctionne l\'essai?',de:'Wie funktioniert die Testversion?',es:'Como funciona la prueba?',it:'Come funziona la prova?',zh:'免费试用如何运作？'},
'How long can each recording be?':{fr:'Duree max?',de:'Max. Aufnahmedauer?',es:'Duracion max?',it:'Durata max?',zh:'每条录音可以多长？'},
'What languages does VoiceNote support?':{fr:'Quelles langues?',de:'Welche Sprachen?',es:'Que idiomas?',it:'Quali lingue?',zh:'支持哪些语言？'},
'VoiceNote supports 46 languages for both transcription and AI polishing, covering major languages across Europe, Asia, the Middle East, and the Americas.':{fr:'VoiceNote prend en charge 46 langues pour la transcription et le polissage IA, couvrant l\'Europe, l\'Asie, le Moyen-Orient et les Ameriques.',de:'VoiceNote unterstutzt 46 Sprachen fur Transkription und KI, in Europa, Asien, Nahost und Amerika.',es:'VoiceNote admite 46 idiomas para transcripcion y pulido IA, cubriendo Europa, Asia, Oriente Medio y America.',it:'VoiceNote supporta 46 lingue per trascrizione e perfezionamento IA, coprendo Europa, Asia, Medio Oriente e Americhe.',zh:'VoiceNote 支持 46 种语言转录和 AI 润色，覆盖欧洲、亚洲、中东和美洲。'},
'Do you offer a refund guarantee?':{fr:'Offrez-vous une garantie?',de:'Ruckerstattung?',es:'Garantia de reembolso?',it:'Garanzia di rimborso?',zh:'有退款保证吗？'},
'Yes. We back all paid plans with a 7-day money-back guarantee. If you\'re not satisfied within the first week, contact support and we\'ll issue a full refund.':{fr:'Oui. Garantie de 7 jours. Pas satisfait? Contactez le support pour un remboursement.',de:'Ja. 7-Tage-Geld-zuruck. Nicht zufrieden? Support fur Ruckerstattung.',es:'Si. Garantia de 7 dias. Si no estas satisfecho, contacta soporte para reembolso.',it:'Si. Garanzia di 7 giorni. Non soddisfatto? Contatta supporto per rimborso.',zh:'是的。7 天退款保证。不满意联系支持全额退款。'},
'Do you offer a refund guarantee?':{fr:'Offrez-vous une garantie?',de:'Ruckerstattung?',es:'Garantia de reembolso?',it:'Garanzia di rimborso?',zh:'有退款保证吗？'},
