'Up to 15 minutes per recording on Prime. That\'s more than enough for meeting recaps, journal entries, brain dumps, and detailed briefs.':{fr:'Jusqu\'a 15 min sur Premium. Ideal pour reunions, journal, brainstorming.',de:'Bis zu 15 Min auf Prime. Genug fur Meetings, Tagebuch, Brainstorming.',es:'Hasta 15 min en Premium. Suficiente para reuniones, diario, ideas.',it:'Fino a 15 min su Premium. Abbastanza per riunioni, diario, brainstorming.',zh:'高级版最长 15 分钟。足以应对会议记录、日记、头脑风暴和简报。'},
'Your first 10 notes are completely free (up to 2 minutes each). No credit card required. After that, choose a Prime plan to keep recording.':{fr:'Vos 10 premieres notes sont gratuites (2 min max). Sans CB. Ensuite, choisissez Premium.',de:'Ihre ersten 10 Notizen sind kostenlos (2 Min). Keine Karte. Danach Prime wahlen.',es:'Tus 10 primeras notas son gratis (2 min). Sin tarjeta. Luego, elige Premium.',it:'Le tue prime 10 note sono gratis (2 min). Nessuna carta. Poi scegli Premium.',zh:'前 10 条笔记免费（每条 2 分钟）。无需信用卡。之后选择高级版继续使用。'},
