// Pricing FAQ answers
'Absolutely. You can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel directly from the app. Changes take effect at the end of your current billing period.':{fr:'Absolument. Mettez a niveau ou annulez depuis l\'app. Les changements prennent effet a la fin de la periode.',de:'Ja. Andern Sie direkt in der App. Anderungen werden zum Ende des Abrechnungszeitraums wirksam.',es:'Por supuesto. Cambia o cancela desde la app. Los cambios se aplican al final del periodo.',it:'Certamente. Aggiorna o annulla dall\'app. Le modifiche hanno effetto alla fine del periodo.',zh:'当然。可以直接从 App 升级或取消。变更在当前周期结束时生效。'},
'Your first 10 notes are completely free (up to 2 minutes each). No credit card required. After that, choose a Prime plan to keep recording.':{fr:'Vos 10 premieres notes sont gratuites (2 min max). Sans CB. Ensuite, choisissez Prime.',de:'Ihre ersten 10 Notizen sind kostenlos. Keine Kreditkarte. Danach Prime wahlen.',es:'Tus 10 primeras notas son gratis. Sin tarjeta. Luego, elige Prime.',it:'Le tue prime 10 note sono gratis. Nessuna carta. Poi scegli Prime.',zh:'前 10 条笔记完全免费（每条 2 分钟）。无需信用卡。之后选 Prime。'},
'Your notes are yours. If you cancel, you\'ll still have read-only access to all your existing notes. You can export them anytime.':{fr:'Vos notes sont a vous. Si vous annulez, acces en lecture seule conserve. Exportez a tout moment.',de:'Ihre Notizen gehoren Ihnen. Nach Kundigung Lesezugriff. Export jederzeit moglich.',es:'Tus notas son tuyas. Si cancelas, acceso de solo lectura. Exporta cuando quieras.',it:'Le tue note sono tue. Se annulli, accesso in sola lettura. Esporta quando vuoi.',zh:'笔记属于你。取消后仍可只读访问，随时导出。'},
'Up to 15 minutes per recording on Prime. That\'s more than enough for meeting recaps, journal entries, brain dumps, and detailed briefs.':{fr:'Jusqu\'a 15 min sur Prime. Ideal pour reunions, journal, brainstorming.',de:'Bis zu 15 Min auf Prime. Genug fur Meetings, Tagebuch, Brainstorming.',es:'Hasta 15 min en Prime. Suficiente para reuniones, diario, ideas.',it:'Fino a 15 min su Prime. Abbastanza per riunioni, diario, brainstorming.',zh:'Prime 最长 15 分钟。足以应对会议、日记和头脑风暴。'},
